triana.types

Class Const

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Number
      • triana.types.Const
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable, Arithmetic

    public class Const
extends java.lang.Number
implements Arithmetic, java.lang.Comparable
    Const is a wrapper for basic base number types e.g. int, float, long, short and double. It stores a single real or complex number of one of those types.
    See Also:
